The paper deals with the task of generating descriptive documents from data records, which falls under the domain of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses neural generation methods, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The evaluation methods proposed in the paper involve extractive analysis, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with data records, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.DB (Databases).
